@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (0.95 - ((tmp + 0.98 - tmp + 0.07) - wp.sin(v0 + 0.69)))
    v0 = tmp
    v0 = tmp
    tmp = wp.sin(((v2 + 0.08 + v1 + 0.76) * wp.abs(v0 + 0.83)))
    v2 = wp.abs(wp.cos(wp.exp(v1 + 0.13)))
    tmp = wp.exp((wp.cos(v1 + 1.00) * wp.abs(tmp + 0.19)))
    v1 = v0
    tmp = 0.56
    data[tid] = v0
